{"tid":1622254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位唔好中柒婆嘅計","createTime":"2019-10-04T15:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T17:46:11.000Z","uid":55964,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44d519aaa7492fbffc571d7907c1672f803f39f2","tid":1622254,"uid":55964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"林奠明知蒙面法會激起咁大民憤都要硬推，唔係因為佢蠢<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為佢想一次過拉哂我地翻去呀</span></span></strong><br />\n政府已經冇耐性再等，佢硬推呢條惡法<br />\n係因為睇準我地心態一定會覺得Now Or Never、「你唔比我蒙面我就蒙面走哂出黎」<br />\n咁佢就可以無差別，務求最快拉哂我地珍貴嘅前線手足<br />\n營造抗爭事件暫告一段落嘅假象<br />\n又或者嚇到其他和理非唔岀嚟！<br />\n<br />\n但大家唔好中計，留有用之驅同佢慢慢磨<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">堅守不被捕原則！</span></span></strong><br />\n唔好有endgame心態，我地打嘅係長線抗爭<br />\n每一次嘅抗爭都等於政府多一日嘅失敗<br />\n我地繼續用經濟手段制裁中資，繼續每日十八區集結，繼續裝修中資企業，直至香港重光<br />\n<br />\n所以今晚大家唔好死守，嚟緊仲有好多抗爭嘅路！<br />\n求下大家，前線手足一個都不能少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係散水撚，但唔想大家中林奠嘅計"},{"pid":"0b567dfcc7724450ed8f75fdd23d7fb2d32dd9d7","tid":1622254,"uid":114487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命 香港獨立<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZgexrEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZgexrEO.jpg&h=b11612da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZhfpru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZhfpru.jpg&h=7bbe8894&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0abed75d5df34106786b4ca497f43df6c7732d5","tid":1622254,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"12點前張床要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid